<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉nạ mḥtạj lmsẗ rwḥk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 (ạ̉nạ mḥtạj lmsẗ rwḥk .. tgẖyrny
 wạnạ mḥtạj yạ yswʿ dmk .. yṭhrny)2
 (wạnạ lmạ hậjy .. wạsẖwfk
 wạsẖwf ạsmy .. ʿly̱ kfwfk
 btfk ạlạ̉sr wḥqk .. byḥrrny)2
 (ạ̹n knt ḍʿyf .. qwyny
 ạ̹n knt ḥzyn .. ʿzyny
 ạ̹n knt kẖạṭy .. ạ̹brỷny wạsẖfyny
 ạ̹lmsny bslṭạnk .. wryny mjd jlạlk
 ạ̉gẖmr qlby bḥnạnk .. wạrwyny)2</lyrics>
